	"DISTRIBUTOR_FAQ_4":"Our distribution center receives shipments from numerous manufacturers. In the event of a product malfunction, identifying the producer can be very important. Does YARRAA provide information on products? point of origin?",
	"DISTRIBUTOR_FAQ_ANS_4":"Yes. YARRAA provides all the relevant information on each individual item entered into the system, including the time and location of manufacture. This enables you to pinpoint and eliminate flaws in the manufacturing process more quickly.",
